channel.title: Some interface IDs please
channel.description:
I'm doing a complete 100% tutorial island so I need some interface IDs that I don't have:
When you speak to the survival expert, she gives you a hatchet and a tinderbox. -The interface is a regular dialogue box with a hatchet and tinderbox on. -The dialogue box with the logs on (after you cut them) -The dialogue box with a fishing net (When the survival expert gives you one) -The dialogue box with the flour and bucket on from the master chef -The dialogue box when Derek gives you a bronze pickaxe -The dialogue box when you retreive a hammer
So and and so forth, all the interfaces when guides give you items. If anyone knows one, any or all the IDs please post here. Thanks <3
